@DATABASE "Shadow Of The Beast"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - S - Shadow Of The Beast"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - S
                   ====================================

                            Shadow Of The Beast
                            ===================



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Energy" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(33220,0)"}         33220,0
@{"Energy = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(25143,255) zxampoke(29880,255)"}         25143,x:29880,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
